---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="border-t border-[var(--color-rule)] mt-20">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-10 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
    <div>
      <p class="font-serif text-base text-[var(--color-ink)]">dudewheresmylikeness.com</p>
      <p class="mt-1 max-w-md">
        A public watchtower for AI likeness rights. Built by
        <a href="https://www.gsb.stanford.edu/programs/msx" class="underline">Daniel Etzioni</a>,
        drawing on executive interviews at CAA, WME, and UTA.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="md:text-right">
      <p class="uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">Not legal advice</p>
      <p class="mt-1 max-w-md md:ml-auto">
        Information on this site is editorial and for orientation only. Nothing here
        constitutes legal advice. Consult qualified counsel for your jurisdiction.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xs">&copy; {year}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
